For success using this app:
    1) Select option with Rover(Curiosity, Opportunity or Spirit);
    2) Select option with Camera(Front, Rear, â€¦)
    3) Enter Sol (Mars day) in numbers (min 1, max 1000)
    This options are must have to enter!

    4) If your fields aren't you should press on button "GET PHOTOS"
    Finilly) You get photos and you can slide your photos.
    If you press on right photo part, photo will be changed on next photo.
    Go back to previous? press on left photo part

    For one more selection of photos - refresh the web page and enter anouther data:) 
    
